overview: Grand Prize Chevrolet of Miami is the leading Chevy dealership serving Kendall, South Miami, and all of South Florida. Whether you’re in various parts of Southern Florida or right here in Miami, we know you’ll enjoy our new and used Chevrolet vehicles, our competitive financing, GM-certified parts, and our extensive auto service. Visit us today and get your next car, truck, or SUV! We specialize in the Chevy Silverado.
